reviewText: Got this for Christmas for my daughter, she loves dinosaurs.  Arrived on time for her to open on Christmas day however when we tried to play the DVD, it was "incompatible" with all 3 dvd players and our XBOX.  I would return it but like most kid things it disappeared in the black hole.
Jeff Goldblum  tells you all about them and he has a nice voice for it. And it has a lot of information.
